title: Tannehill helps Dolphins improve to 2-0 under coach Campbell
text:
> Texas Tannehill helps Dolphins improve to 2-0 under coach Campbell Miami Dolphins quarterback Ryan Tannehill (17) looks to pass during the first half of an NFL football game against the Houston Texans, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015 in Miami Gardens, Fla. The Dolphins defeated the Texans 44-26. Tannehill set an NFL record by completing a series of passes over two games.
